[30/05/2019 11:25:51] <font color="#ffffff">Por el día.</font>
[30/05/2019 11:26:04] <font color="#ffffff">De noche...</font>
[30/05/2019 11:26:04] <font color="#ffffff">es otro mundo.</font>
[30/05/2019 11:26:11] <font color="#ffffff">Un cangrejo anda ala caza</font>
